snippet.title: ADEN 2024 Trailer
snippet.description:
亜電"Aden" is a Japanese indie game.
It is a completely new belt-scrolling game based on the concept of battle, kawaii and dance.
It will be released on Steam in 2024.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2152740
